Type: Package
Package: scientific
Title: Elegant Scientific Themed Reporting for 'Markdown'
Version: 2024.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Obinna", "Obianom", email = "idonshayo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Obinna Obianom <idonshayo@gmail.com>
Description: Offers 'markdown' output formats designed with various scientific styles, allowing users to generate PDF and HTML outputs. The output has a contemporary appearance with vibrant visuals, providing numerous styles for effective highlighting. The package also includes additional features specifically tailored for front-page slides, enhancing the overall presentation and customization options. The package was created using the 'tufte' R package code as a starting point.
